{"tid":2413723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"軍方鎖網？緬甸黑客入侵政府及官媒網站還擊！","createTime":"2021-02-19T02:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T03:34:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31ba8aab2320207cfae82a8bb0be4d7eb03f6b2e","tid":2413723,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T02:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/-_953481917602e4a1e6cd27-1000x600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F-_953481917602e4a1e6cd27-1000x600.jpg&h=38d03397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緬甸軍方封鎖互聯網以打壓群眾示威及反對聲音，黑客組織「緬甸黑客」(Myanmar Hackers)發動網攻反擊，入侵多個緬甸政府部門以及與軍方關係密切的網站，導致網站癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n英國的互聯網斷網事故監察組織NetBlocks指，緬甸軍方當地時間周四凌晨1時起再封鎖互聯網，是連續第四晚「鎖網」。緬甸網媒The Irrawaddy報道，緬甸中央銀行、軍方經營的Tatmadaw真新聞資訊組、Myawady TV以及貿易部網站，於周三早上無法登入。「緬甸黑客」其後在Facebook(FB)貼文承認發動網攻，帖文指「我們目的是推翻軍政權，我們會在網上作戰，去摧毀支撐軍政權的核心部門和產業」。帖文並稱「我們為緬甸的公義而戰，就像在政府網站前舉行大型群眾示威一樣」。「緬甸黑客」FB專頁還分享連結，稱可透過該連結對緬甸軍方網站發動網攻，並呼籲網友加入：「用你們自己的雙手去入侵，加入攻擊。」<br />\n<br />\nThe Irrawaddy報道，緬甸商務部、海關部門、國營廣播機構「緬甸電台及電視」以及部分私營傳媒網站都被入侵。仰光一名電腦技術員指，這次黑客攻擊令目標網站流量大增，致其癱瘓。"},{"pid":"d2c294f3a35a7d71ea433bc347761d97adc333b9","tid":2413723,"uid":256019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"美國佬快d普及全球衛星WIFI，到時睇你班畜牲點撚樣鎖網！"},{"pid":"3da79a66b922fc7891456c79d5106a8f1be5b3a8","tid":2413723,"uid":347528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"香港黑客呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1154d577d44397777bd9483ab637a4d6df8b951","tid":2413723,"uid":27432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"anonymous 呢"},{"pid":"5c00e63a113c00a11860abd90fae5bef539b28b0","tid":2413723,"uid":33456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"香港著名黑客Net Send呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ea8154fbfc506f04c68333ad01316ec553e5d8","tid":2413723,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3da79a66b922fc7891456c79d5106a8f1be5b3a8","tid":2413723,"uid":347528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"香港黑客呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:26:10.000Z","msg":"唔太記得有無做嘢<br />\n<br />\n印象中, 好似係零星DDOS"},{"pid":"fbd655353e836179c34d675c5a69fe098dcafbf1","tid":2413723,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58ea8154fbfc506f04c68333ad01316ec553e5d8","tid":2413723,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3da79a66b922fc7891456c79d5106a8f1be5b3a8","tid":2413723,"uid":347528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"香港黑客呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:26:10.000Z","msg":"唔太記得有無做嘢<br />\n<br />\n印象中, 好似係零星DDOS"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:34:06.000Z","msg":"HK no IT <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}